# Leave VITE_API_BASE_URL unset (or empty) to run the frontend against
# mock data — see src/lib/api/mocks/. This is the default for local
# development before the backend (see /backend in the project root) is deployed.
#
# Once the AssetWave backend (docs/api_design.md) is running, set this
# to its base URL and the app will automatically switch from mocks to
# live API calls — no component code changes required.
#
# Example:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:4000/v1
VITE_API_BASE_URL=
